    <title>github page 教學</title>
    <link href="/2022/09/04/hello-world-1/"/>
    <url>/2022/09/04/hello-world-1/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="guide"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#guide"></a> guide</h1><ol><li><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/371995929">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/371995929</a></li><li><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/juzaizai/p/14472119.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/juzaizai/p/14472119.html</a></li></ol><h2 id="theme"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#theme"></a> theme</h2><ul><li>next</li><li>fluid<ul><li><a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid</a></li><li>Hexo Fluid用戶手冊: <a href="https://fluid-dev.github.io/hexo-fluid-docs/guide/#%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97">https://fluid-dev.github.io/hexo-fluid-docs/guide/#关于指南</a></li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="圖片"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#圖片"></a> 圖片</h2><p>Ref: <a href="https://blog.51cto.com/alexclownfish/3051079">https://blog.51cto.com/alexclownfish/3051079</a></p><ul><li>插入圖片，不可調整大小：  <div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs arcade">![](<span class="hljs-regexp">/img/</span>example.jpg)</code></pre></div></li><li>插入圖片，可調整大小  <div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs awk">![](https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>alexcld.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/images/</span>pengyuyan.jpg)</code></pre></div></li></ul><h2 id="codeblock"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#codeblock"></a> codeblock</h2><p>Ref: <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/35441138/how-do-i-insert-this-code-into-a-hexo-markdown">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/35441138/how-do-i-insert-this-code-into-a-hexo-markdown</a></p><h1 id="problems-solve"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#problems-solve"></a> problems &amp; solve</h1><ul><li>hexo – 遠端更新<ul><li>hexo clean -&gt; hexo g -d</li></ul></li><li>hexo – po新文章，遠端不顯示<ul><li>等待(因為更新有延遲)</li><li>清除緩存 Crtl + F5</li></ul></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
